{"type": "article", "id": 24937, "title": "带海鸟的啤酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-05T07:03:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121007osPhkTN0pBnfIVEC.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个来自瑞典的啤酒包装上有着一只令人印象深刻的鸟，瓶盖上是鸟头的图案，瓶身的贴纸和装啤酒的纸箱上是张开翅膀的鸟的剪影，使得整体包装完整且有强烈的辨识度。鸟的图案指的是酿造的地方 Sibbarp，除此之外也没有其他的图案，给人带来一种传统手工的感受。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071210047ZEd34UeBGMmgRLs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75049702\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121005oAZMdtXTIcOJ8eyB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65308151\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121005jZGh4M9PgtpeBnv8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121006WADrqTeQLYSx6Fzh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121006QEIRkoacMl3HjA0t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121007Pgqyjsfa9wSK6ZMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}